possiveis erros com audio input virtualbox ubuntu guest:

audio config: under tab Applications, enable Alsa plug-in [python...]

pulseaudio -k && sudo alsa force-reload

--------------------------------------------------------------

make audio input default inpulseaudio:-----------------------------------------------------
pactl list short sources
copy the name and insert 
set-default-source alsa_input.usb-Plantronics_Plantronics_Headset_00050-0504044410003-V060000D-00.analog-stereo
in: 
sudo gedit /etc/pulse/default.pa
apparently as soon one clicks the Vmachine to start, have to click Devices-USB-Plantronics... so that the audio input is initialized in time as default
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

